{"tid":2141840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★ 明起入境廣東須24小時內檢測證明 大批支鬼趕回支那！","createTime":"2020-08-06T04:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T22:21:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":282,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"22618dd08ebb020bbda681075f0ed8a9912dcc00","tid":2141840,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:15:38.000Z","msg":"在早上，有二十多人在屯門巴士站等候往深圳灣的頭班車，有市民表示有關新安排很難做到，所以提早返回內地。  市民楊先生表示：「本來想明天(出發)，預計不到昨晚上網見到要24小時、明天開始，我就提早今日，都無辦法，要看情況。」  被問到會不會減少回港或去內地，及會減少多少，他指：「肯定會，我想九成。」  被問及本來是否一個月一次，他稱：「是，現在我想最快都三個月。」  市民陳女士指：「迫到人好趕，如果真的是24小時，可能時間會好緊迫，好緊迫，過關甚至是趕不到。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5f2b794134b031fd7e28f553/港人明起入境廣東須持24小時內檢測證明-有港人提早回深圳\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5f2b794134b031fd7e28f553%2F%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%98%8E%E8%B5%B7%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E9%A0%88%E6%8C%8124%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%85%A7%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E-%E6%9C%89%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%8F%90%E6%97%A9%E5%9B%9E%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=2a586d3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5f2b794134b031fd7e28f553/港人明起入境廣東須持24小時內檢測證明-有港人提早回深圳</a>"},{"pid":"b53189e2024812521f33919ddedfbc0c964bda8f","tid":2141840,"uid":19454,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nnever come back"},{"pid":"6055734f8660676ec832d01d4f95d3e9d8e4d127","tid":2141840,"uid":312363,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"c